name: Renjana Pagebluk
description: The term Renjana is passion (spark of interest). This passion describes the madness of the pandemic that is going on. In 2019, we were brought in by a virus which is still taking the lives of several of our brothers and sisters. The madness of the pandemic continues to run rampant until 2020, and in 2022 we are welcomed back by a new variant of the virus. I don't know how long this pandemic passion will end. Let's pray together, take care and protect each other.
